description: Try our easy to follow Whiting Burgers With Pickled Onion recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Whiting Burgers With Pickled Onion Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 pkt 425 Birds Eye Southern Blue Whiting Original Crumb

recipeInstructions.text: Bake Birds Eye Sourthern Blue Whiting Original Crumb fish fillets according to packet instructions, then stack in toasted brioche buns with gem lettuce leaves, cucumber ribbons, aioli and pickled red onion. Serve with oven-baked chips.
